examples.en: A car sped past in a cloud of dust.
He jumped into his car and sped off.
A shooting star sped across the sky.
A group of kids sped past us on their bikes.
She sped up the process by eliminating all extraneous steps.
The car sped by at a whopping 110 miles per hour.
An ambulance sped her to the hospital.
We glimpsed him through the window as his car sped past.
He jammed his foot on the accelerator and the car sped off.
We caught a glimpse of him through the window as his car sped past.
He sped up and averted an accident.
The car left a trail of smoke as it sped off.
The car sped along the dusty highway.
They jumped in the car and sped away.
